section.section:
Unless authorized by law to possess the substance, a person may not bring into the State:
45 kilograms or more of marijuana;
28 grams or more of cocaine;
any mixture containing 28 grams or more of cocaine;
4 grams or more of morphine or opium or any derivative, salt, isomer, or salt of an isomer of morphine or opium;
1,000 dosage units of lysergic acid diethylamide;
any mixture containing the equivalent of 1,000 dosage units of lysergic acid diethylamide;
28 grams or more of phencyclidine in liquid or powder form;
112 grams or more of any mixture containing phencyclidine;
1,000 dosage units or more of methaqualone;
28 grams or more of methamphetamine;
any mixture containing 28 grams or more of methamphetamine; or
4 grams or more of fentanyl or a fentanyl analogue.
